# =============================================================================
# Docker build context exclusions.
#
# The Rhitta API image is built from the *monorepo root* (so pnpm has the
# workspace + lockfile + cross-package source it needs). That makes the
# raw context huge by default — this file trims it down to the artifacts
# the build actually needs.
#
# Mirrors .gitignore where it makes sense, plus build-tool caches that
# are tracked by git but never useful inside a container.
# =============================================================================

# --- Version control & CI metadata ------------------------------------------
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github

# --- Dependencies (installed fresh inside the image) ------------------------
node_modules
**/node_modules
.pnpm-store
**/.pnpm-store

# --- Build output -----------------------------------------------------------
dist
**/dist
build
**/build
out
**/out
.next
**/.next
.turbo
**/.turbo
.cache
**/.cache
.parcel-cache
**/.parcel-cache
*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Encore CLI workspace-local install (created by scripts/build-docker.sh
# on CI; never belongs inside the image).
.encore
**/.encore

# Encore-generated runtime stubs (regenerated by `encore build docker`).
**/encore.gen

# --- Secrets — NEVER ship -------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# --- Logs -------------------------------------------------------------------
*.log
**/*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# --- Tests, fixtures, dev tooling ------------------------------------------
coverage
**/coverage
.nyc_output
**/.nyc_output
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx
**/__tests__
**/__fixtures__
**/__mocks__
vitest.config.ts
**/vitest.config.ts
vitest.setup.ts
**/vitest.setup.ts

# --- Editor & OS noise ------------------------------------------------------
.idea
.vscode
.cursor
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Documentation (huge, never used at runtime) ---------------------------
docs
*.md
!apps/api/**/*.md

# --- Other apps don't belong in the API image ------------------------------
apps/web
apps/mobile

# --- Misc -------------------------------------------------------------------
*.tmp
*.bak
.changeset
